🤹Paper 
🤹Scissors 
🤹Sketch pen /printer
🤹Speaker 
🤹Choose a place where kid can run 

🤹Print / write the activities on different pieces of paper
🤹Cut the paper into different shapes
Place the cards on the floor in a circle 
🤹When you choose song choose any rhyme the toddler has to run from one card to another 
🤹When the music stops toddler has to perform the activity mentioned on the card he / she stops at ! (You might have to enact that activity first)
🤹To keep the energy high use differ rhyme at different round
